text: Khosheutovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Khosheutovsky Selsoviet, Kharabalinsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 2,097 as of 2010. There are 29 streets. == Geography == It is located 91 km from Astrakhan, 71 km from Kharabali. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kharabalinsky District
title: Khosheutovo
